		"AbilityTooltips"
		{
			"special_bonus_unique_viper_2"		"Since you're doubling down on magic damage, it sounds convinient to significantly amplify your ult"
			"viper_nethertoxin"		"Aside from massive damage and magic resistance reduction, this spell is your main farming tool. You just need to max it out early and start farming nearest jungle camp and lane at the same time"
			"viper_poison_attack"		"Poison attack makes a strong laner out of Viper.  You don't really need to level this up more than once, but it's still pretty important to have early on to zone opponent out of lane without drawing aggro from creeps"
			"viper_corrosive_skin"		"Early tankiness solution and another spell that can be useful for farming"
			"viper_viper_strike"		"Massive magic damage (especially in combination with nethertoxin) and undispellable slow. It's almost reliable kill early on except it's possible to TP out from it"
			"special_bonus_spell_lifesteal_8"		"Considering your massive amounts of AoE damage you will be healing a lot from it "
			"special_bonus_unique_viper_1"		"Considering you're playing as a tanky frontliner, there aren't much use from attack range, but having a bit more slow, damage and magic resist will do some work"
			"special_bonus_attack_damage_120"		"If you're planning to transition into physical or hybrid core later on, it may be a good idea to get this talent"
			"special_bonus_unique_viper_3"		"Considering Nethertoxin's cooldown it's usually good idea to make it also AoE silence which will also help against a lot of heroes in fights"
